Instructions on how to run this app

1) Make sure you have the correct expo version installed (4.0 +) 
2) Open the code in your code editor of choice.
3) run npm / yarn install (you only need to this once).
4) run npm start to execute the code.


It is advised that you have an android/IOS emulator or have expo go installed on your smartphone in order to run the app.
(instructions for android https://developer.android.com/studio/run/emulator)
(instructions for ios emulator https://developer.apple.com/library/archive/documentation/IDEs/Conceptual/iOS_Simulator_Guide/GettingStartedwithiOSSimulator/GettingStartedwithiOSSimulator.html)
